What can you do on this site ? : <br>
- search player locations. Push <a href="Players.php?FilterK=67" target="IFShowContent">Players</a> button <br>
- see what guild a player was in the past(spies). Push <a href="Players.php?FilterK=67" target="IFShowContent">Players</a> button, than push a specific player name. <br>
- search hive locations for kill farming. Push <a href="Hives.php" target="IFShowContent">Hives</a> button <br>
- hide <a href="HideTracking.php?Type=Player" target="IFShowContent">you</a> or your <a href="HideTracking.php?Type=Guild" target="IFShowContent">guild</a> to be tracked by this sitte for a period of time<br>
- search for best location for a new hive. Push <a href="pcount_67.html" target="IFShowContent">least players</a> minimap button<br>
- search for worst location for a new hive. Push <a href="might_67.html" target="IFShowContent">strongest players</a> minimap button<br>
- check what gears you will be crafting in the future. Push <a href="Gearsets_out.txt" target="IFShowContent">Gearlist</a> button <br>
- see how exactly <a href="CombatStatistics.php" target="IFShowContent">combat</a> works<br>
- check what <a href="changelog.html" target="IFShowContent">changed</a> since you last visited this site<br>
